quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  32,11,"“Nena: “Adzachotsa mizimu yanu Mngelo wa imfa yemwe wapatsidwa udindo umenewu pa inu. Kenako mudzabwerera kwa Mbuye wanu.”"
  32,12,"“Ndipo ukadawaona oipa atazolikitsa mitu yawo kwa Mbuye wawo (uku akunena): “E Mbuye wathu! Taona, ndipo tamva. Choncho tibwezeni tikachita ntchito zabwino. Ndithu tsopano tatsimikiza (kukhulupirira).”"
  32,13,"“Ndipo tikadafuna, tikadaupatsa mzimu ulionse chiongoko chake (moukakamiza monga momwe tidawachitira angelo, koma mzimu udapatsidwa mphamvu ndi ufulu wodzisankhira chimene ufuna; chabwino kapena choipa). Koma mawu atsimikizika ochokera kwa Ine: “Ndithu ndizadzazitsa Jahannam ziwanda ndi anthu; onse pamodzi (amene ali oipa).”"
  32,14,"““Choncho, lawani chifukwa cha kuyiwala (kusalabadila) kwanu kukumana ndi tsiku lanu ili. Ifenso tikusiyani (ku chilango monga ngati takuiwalani). Tero lawani chilango chamuyaya, chifukwa cha zomwe munkachita.”"
  32,15,"“Ndithu amene akukhulupirira Ayah Zathu, ndiamene akuti pamene akukumbutsidwa ndi Ayazo, amagwetsa nkhope zawo pansi (kusujudu) ndi kulemekeza Mbuye wawo pamodzi ndi kumthokoza. Ndipo iwo sadzitukumula"
  32,16,"“Nthiti zawo zimalekana ndi malo ogona (usiku), uku akumpempha Mbuye wawo, moopa ndi mwachiyembekezo. Ndipo amapereka (Zakaat ndi sadaka) mzimene tawapatsa"
  32,17,“Mzimu uliwonse sudziwa zimene aubisira zotonthoza diso (zosangalatsa moyo ku Munda wa mtendere) monga mphoto pa zimene unkachita
  32,18,“Kodi yemwe ali okhulupirira angafanane ndi wotuluka m’chilamulo cha Allah? Sangafanane
  32,19,"“Tsono amene akhulupirira ndi kumachita zabwino, adzalandira Minda yokhalamo yokongola, monga phwando lawo pa zimene ankachita"
  32,20,"“Koma kwa amene adachita zoipa potuluka m’chilamulo cha Allah, malo awo ndi ku Moto. Nthawi iliyonse akafuna kutulukamo, azikabwezedwamo ndipo azidzauzidwa: “Lawani chilango cha Moto, chomwe munkachitsutsa.”"
  32,21,"“Ndipo ndithudi, tiwalawitsa chilango chocheperapo (pa dziko lapansi) chisanafike chilango chachikulu (cha tsiku lachimaliziro), kuti atembenuke, (alape)"
  32,22,"“Kodi ndani wachinyengo kwambiri, woposa yemwe akukumbutsidwa Ayah za Mbuye wake, kenako nkuzikana? Ndithu Ife, tidzawabwezera zoipa anthu oipa"
  32,23,“Ndipo ndithu Mûsa tidampatsa buku. Choncho usakhale ndi chikaiko pa zakukumana Naye (Allah). Ndipo tidalichita (bukulo) kukhala chiongoko cha ana a Israyeli
  32,24,"“Ndipo ena mwa iwo tidawachita kukhala atsogoleri oongola (anthu) mwa lamulo lathu, pamene adapirira; ndipo adali kuvomereza motsimikiza Ayah Zathu"
  32,25,“Ndithudi Mbuye wako ndi Yemwe adzaweruze pakati pawo tsiku la Qiyâma pazimene amatsutsana
  32,26,"“Kodi sizidadziwike kwa iwo kuti ndimibadwo ingati imene tidaiononga patsogolo pawo; (chikhalirecho iwo) akudutsa mokhala mwawo? Ndithu m’zimenezo, muli zizindikiro, kodi sakumva"
  32,27,“Kodi sakuona kuti timapereka madzi ku nthaka youma; ndipo ndi madziwo tikumeretsa mrnera umene ziweto zawo zimadya ndi iwo omwe; kodi sakupenya
  32,28,"“Ndipo akunena: “Kulamulidwa kumeneku (kwa tsiku la chimaliziro) kudzachitika liti, ngati mukunenadi zoona?”"
  32,29,"“Nena: “Tsiku la chiweruzirolo, amene sadakhulupirire, chikhulupiriro chawo sichidzawathandiza. Ndipo sadzapatsidwa nthawi yoyembekezera (kuti mizimu yawo isachoke ayambe akhulupirira kaye, mngero wa imfa akadzawadzera).”"
  32,30,“Choncho apatuke; ndipo yembekezera (zimene Allah wakulonjeza). Ndithu nawonso akuyembekezera (zimene Allah wawalonjeza)